Carnival Cravings with Anthony Anderson - Season 1, Episode 4




Bacon-Wrapped Heartland

Anthony Anderson eats his way through the heartland at Prairie Fest in Oswego, Ill., gobbling up everything from bacon-wrapped roasted corn to a twist on a local specialty, a Chicago crab dog. Then, it's an Anderson family reunion as Anthony runs into his Great Aunt Pearl and ropes her into his carnival culinary quest.




Original Air Date: 02-Sep-2015
